---
title: Mexican-Style Bacon & Black Bean Burrito Bowl with Avocado, Sour Cream & Tomato Salsa
description: Embark on a culinary fiesta with our Mexican burrito bowl, where black beans are simmered in a tomato-based sauce and served alongside a zestytomato salsa and cooling sour cream. This vibrant bowl is a symphony of flavours, delivering a taste of Mexico in every satisfying bite!
